Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.25,0:00:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.32,0:00:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.13,0:00:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.57,0:00:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.74,0:00:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.79,0:00:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.16,0:00:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.99,0:00:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.23,0:00:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.00,0:01:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.32,0:01:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.46,0:01:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.88,0:01:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷勢有沒有好一點呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.88,0:01:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,請來這裡坐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.81,0:01:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我削個蘋果給妳吃吧\N我這裡有好多橘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.65,0:01:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上放音樂給妳聽\N要不要吃一點?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.12,0:01:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來這裡照顧你們的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼吩咐請儘管說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行\N我怎麼可以使喚妳做事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.96,0:01:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.36,0:02:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說有什麼衣服要洗的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.53,0:02:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事他自己來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.00,0:02:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,他都已經說要自己洗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣的話\N我來這裡就沒有意義了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.18,0:02:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要妳的笑容就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.14,0:02:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是最棒的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.41,0:02:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,不要隨便握她的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都很有精神嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來不需要住院吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.05,0:02:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.85,0:02:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說妳一個人大概會忙不過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,你們兩個都把\N要洗的衣服拿出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,這些就麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就有衣服要洗嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.83,0:02:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個請不要對我這麼客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,請不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.20,0:02:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛,像洗衣服這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.84,0:02:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像洗衣服這種事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像洗衣服這種事?\N你這是什麼意思?說來聽聽看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是洗衣機在洗嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.01,0:02:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼轉動洗衣機的是誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.54,0:03:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#43戀愛的火花衝擊\N五代和三鷹住院騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當女人真的很幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個都很可愛嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.96,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個為了救妳而骨折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.47,0:03:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一個則是為了追求妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.51,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可是沒辦法\N像這樣一直逃避的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有逃避啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢\N妳說我在逃避什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,不好意思\N關小聲一點,好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵到你了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在說妳,我說的是五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我把聲音關小一點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.52,0:05:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種不尋常的溫馨氣氛\N是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,要去照X光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.03,0:05:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我陪你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我陪他去就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳堅持要照顧五代\N那我就不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.74,0:05:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有,我沒有那個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.45,0:05:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳小心點\N不要讓他對妳亂來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去啦,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人好像沒什麼信用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.31,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我的確是因為妳在這裡\N才來這裡住院的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像是我白費功夫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.29,0:06:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可笑吧,儘管笑沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會取笑你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開田醫師,開田醫師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.29,0:06:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我,請你放開我\N惣一郎,他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.56,0:06:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻到外科病棟來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.26,0:07:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.01,0:07:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎,我才是被你嚇死了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.71,0:07:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,管理員\N妳剛才叫得好大聲喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.15,0:07:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事?什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.36,0:08:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想點事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎,我們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…我去買點什麼東西回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,請妳休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事情做比較輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要看報紙呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我要體育報紙和漫畫\N不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說,三鷹呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.28,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳帶一份經濟時報和\N一本時事週刊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.22,0:09:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N順便帶點果汁回來比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.82,0:09:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有事情做就覺得很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經好久沒有這樣照顧人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.37,0:09:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹教練,我們來看你了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都不知道你在住院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.41,0:09:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了球場練習\N才知道你請病假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.18,0:09:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好像很痛的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.85,0:09:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些女孩是我在\N女子大學網球社教的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.39,0:09:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你不只受歐巴桑歡迎\N也很受年輕女孩歡迎嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.63,0:09:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,你就不要謙虛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要跟你約會\N還得排上三個月呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經談好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始\N每天輪流來照顧教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦,這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人的好意應該坦率接受喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.08,0:10:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很賴皮耶,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.71,0:10:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要管理員一次照顧兩個人\N也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.82,0:10:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.66,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,一直沒辦法來看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.86,0:10:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N這些日子真是辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前沒有照顧到五代的份\N從今天起我會好好照顧他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人的好意應該坦率接受喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.51,0:10:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我就回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.39,0:10:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道我就不要幫他們想那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.39,0:11:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(笨蛋)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.30,0:11:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去給惣一郎掃墓好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員不來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.24,0:12:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,她說不需要這麼多人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,你們終於出院了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,醫生,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.41,0:12:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.22,0:12:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人能一起出院\N真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再來了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,請多保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.86,0:12:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹了什麼壞事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.20,0:12:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說,都要怪大嬸你們\N跑來醫院玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們接下來要去三鷹教練家\N為他舉行出院派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你們要不要一起來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得呢?五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不去了,現在去的話\N回家會很麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.45,0:12:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,三鷹教練多保重囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家請多保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見囉,五代,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了\N啊,對了對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.55,0:13:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該去接他出院比較好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.46,0:13:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.16,0:13:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣,不要啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,會撞到頭的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.37,0:13:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.91,0:13:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.59,0:14:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.66,0:14:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是從醫院跟來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.92,0:14:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想說他回家之後\N可能也有很多事情要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.50,0:14:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,小津江能跟著你回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也有很多雜事要忙\N無法抽空出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託妳囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.37,0:14:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我們進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛,不要客氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.06,0:14:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦,真的不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.47,0:14:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行,五代你也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.34,0:15:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管他們在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜出院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.62,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,大家盡情喝個痛快\N因為今晚是五代請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.16,0:15:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有錢喔\N因為我才剛出院而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.43,0:15:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先幫你墊錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好妳個頭啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.25,0:15:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,不要窩在角落\N到這裡來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不行\N現在的管理員不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這又是為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了替死去的丈夫守寡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像突然想了起來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼現在才在說這個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳現在不想接近男人,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟死人是不會背叛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.90,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.58,0:16:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我又有靈感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚴冬窩在家裡\N野獸和蟲兒也都躲在洞穴裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.48,0:16:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要時間一過\N管理員也會從窩身的洞穴出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原本樂觀地想著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代說今天要去醫院複檢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就陪他去吧,他會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有公寓的事情要處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.62,0:17:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能只顧著照料五代一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.40,0:17:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.80,0:17:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是今天複檢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.86,0:18:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,這麼說自從出院以後\N音無小姐都一直不理你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什麼儘管點\N今天我請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,音無小姐也真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.51,0:19:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常大概多久會和好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.55,0:19:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!你們不是已經和好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有說過那種話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.02,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此,難怪我覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.49,0:19:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不可能這麼簡單就能和好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.47,0:19:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她很頑固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,真稀奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.53,0:19:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,真的很稀奇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.57,0:19:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確很稀奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.47,0:19:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪這麼晚還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.81,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,討厭\N都已經這個時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.27,0:20:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說,我跟小津江\N連接吻都沒吻過喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.15,0:20:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手也是偶爾牽一下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.05,0:20:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是管理員卻完全都不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.82,0:20:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是跟那些女孩們\N約過會而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又沒做什麼見不得人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.79,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你同時跟幾十個\N幾百個幾千個女孩在交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.10,0:20:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她應該對你更冷淡\N比我更冷淡百倍千倍萬倍才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.17,0:20:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是她的自由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.51,0:20:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.45,0:20:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為響子會把所有的事\N都從她自己的角度去想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹也還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼惣一郎嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.01,0:21:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊\N真希望她清楚表明態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.98,0:21:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼替她著想\N她卻越來越囂張,真是不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好跟她說清楚才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.99,0:21:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說…跟她說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.09,0:21:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能再讓她瞧不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.96,0:21:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.31,0:21:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一班下行電車即將出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.95,0:21:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘客請快上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.80,0:22:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,你這個混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.40,0:22:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.27,0:22:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子也是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.11,0:22:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太沒精神了,再說一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.01,0:22:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響…響子是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.51,0:22:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.68,0:22:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們快點出去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.05,0:22:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.69,0:22:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,借我一根拐杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.46,0:22:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.06,0:22:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放在電車裡,忘了帶出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.46,0:22:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,幹得好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.66,0:22:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧\N不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.11,0:22:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要跟她說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.48,0:22:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能看到她驚訝的表情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.88,0:22:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要說喔,一言為定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.98,0:22:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很煩耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.20,0:23:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.03,0:23:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好擔心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.41,0:23:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.28,0:23:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.92,0:23:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這傢伙在的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.99,0:23:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的腳還好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.96,0:23:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是笨蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.64,0:23:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一本收藏在鐘台樓閣裡的\N老舊相簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.54,0:23:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的?還是假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.71,0:23:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些照片意味著什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.85,0:23:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.65,0:24:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「賢太郎也嚇到臉色發青?\N四谷恐怖的真面目」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.75,0:24:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想\N我們對四谷的事,真的一無所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.20,0:24:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.57,0:24:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.68,0:24:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.42,0:24:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.90,0:24:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.27,0:24:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.00,0:24:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.84,0:25:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.08,0:25:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.02,0:25:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.16,0:25:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.30,0:25:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
